{"tid":342833,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"硬件撚 討論硬件知識、砌機list、解答問題集中帖(36）","createTime":"2017-08-01T02:51:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-06T13:51:57.000Z","uid":7172,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7d073a43a07e1c8ce8cef8117f2feb6e0a3cad42","tid":342833,"uid":7172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:51:11.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新人求List需知</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為方面眾爸打可以好好幫助你<br />\n請你也需好好合作<br />\n不但可以盡快回復你的問題<br />\n更可以令條List更適合你所需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 電腦主要用途 <br />\n純打機，定還需要直播和拍片等功能<br />\n<br />\n2. 目標<br />\n砌機為左玩咩GAME，玩咩類型(Steam有過千萬隻GAME，講清楚想邊一隻)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n過求性價比?晝質效能(高，中，低，全開)?想未來幾年不用再更新電腦?超頻能力?<br />\n<br />\n4. 筆直<br />\n如果你筆直上限好寬鬆一定要講明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 現在或將會便用MON的類型(1080P?2K?4K?144HZ?)<br />\n你既MON其實會限制硬件效能，哪怕再勁既電腦，但用不適合MON的話....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 自己都學習一些<br />\n講真，有一班爸打們好撚憎伸手黨，只需做多一兩步<br />\n哪怕你直接照抄悠二巴打List放上黎問，佢地都會出手幫助<br />\n只是Ctrl C和Ctrl V咁簡單，大家都會開心既事點解唔做呢<br />\n甚至可能你在過程中已經搵到需要的答案都不一定!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(悠二List網站 : <a href=\"http://yujihw.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com%2F&d=WGN%2F9b88i5SI2hUCuOKJsAdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=76bfed54\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n7. 有信仰請出聲<br />\n廢事巴打們出完條LIST呢樣唔要嗰樣又唔要，當然你可能會浪費了一個更好的選擇"},{"pid":"f960481d6917712888f476627eb6f68a2c5b10ab","tid":342833,"uid":7172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T02:54:48.000Z","msg":"硬件撚 討論硬件知識、砌機list、解答問題集中帖(36)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/342834/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/342834/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"1df633c78f8f0fef90c2888b57b71c0cedc1ffbc","tid":342833,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T13:51:57.000Z","msg":"LM"}]}